(189, 'Who is Filian', '<font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\"><b style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">Filian</b><span style=\\\"font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">&nbsp;is an independent&nbsp;</span><a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\\\" class=\\\"external text\\\" href=\\\"https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/kemonomimi#English\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">kemonomimi</a><span style=\\\"font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">&nbsp;VTuber based in North America, with English being her main broadcasting language. Self-branded as \\\"VTuber alpha\\\" or \\\"VTuber in training,\\\" Filian has not yet made an official debut, though she has been streaming on Twitch since 18 April 2021. Filian also has an alter ego named Gilian, who is similar to Filian but wears different outfits and has long bluish-purplish hair.<br><br></span></font><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 6px 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; overflow: auto; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"Bio\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Bio</font></span></h2><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Hiya!</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">So basically I do flips for fruit snacks, function as a top tier TTS bot, emit gremlin noises, and have heart attacks--then I call it a stream!</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">I stream VR Chat, variety games, and my inevitable descent into insanity! Height is approximately two pens tall.</font></p><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 6px 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; overflow: auto; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"Personality\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Personality</font></span></h2><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Filian is a very energetic streamer with a cheerful and confident personality. While a fully functioning adult,<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-9\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Filian#cite_note-9\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[note 1]</a></sup>&nbsp;she is not above immature humor, likes playing pranks, and doesn\\\'t like taking things too seriously. She is also very clumsy, often running into walls/objects or falling over.</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Filian tries to maintain a \\\"family-friendly\\\" image, and rarely swears<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-10\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Filian#cite_note-10\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[note 2]</a></sup>&nbsp;and tries not to engage in lewd behavior<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-11\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Filian#cite_note-11\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[note 3]</a></sup>. She is very daring, going through with ridiculous \\\"punishments\\\" which often involve embarrassing herself in public worlds in VRChat, ingesting undesirable combinations of food items, tweeting out self-damaging statements, and more.</font></p><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 6px 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; overflow: auto; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"Appearance\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Appearance</font></span></h2><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Being a VRChat streamer, Filian switches between different 3D models fairly often, but the two most used by her are Mint (also known as Lil\\\' Fil) and Rindo (both customized to have a consistent color scheme). Filian is a cat girl with white hair of varying length depending on the model, and violet eyes. She is small in stature and has a slim body build, evident by the fact that during her first PO Box stream she was able to put on kids\\\' size clothes.</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Her current main model, Rindo, has quite a few outfits. She switches between these outfits often, sometimes going through multiple costumes in one stream. These include:</font></p><ul style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 6px 0px 18px 36px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Japanese-style clothes with detached sleeves</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Sailor/seifuku school uniform</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Long-sleeve black sportswear</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Tennis costume</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Winter outfit with a scarf and earmuffs</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Japanese girls\\\' gym uniform</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Hip-hop costume</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Cat onesie</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Winter hood with shoulder covering</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Race Queen outfit</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">V-neck sweater outfit with a hat</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Business suit</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">One-piece dress</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Elbow sleeve shirt with plaid skirt</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Police officer outfit</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Autumn outfit</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Bikini (seen very rarely)</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Maid costume</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Bunny girl outfit (allegedly retired)</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Idol outfit</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Casual outfit</font></li><li style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Goth outfit with headphones</font></li></ul><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">After her eventual official debut, Filian plans to have a fully custom model, made specifically for her.</font></p><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 6px 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; overflow: auto; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"Content\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Content</font></span></h2><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Unlike the majority of VTubers, Filian almost always streams with full body tracking, and rather than having her model mostly in one place (simulating a webcam, customary for a VTuber), she actively moves around the screen, uses interactive elements (such as VRChat games), and performs gymnastic moves. She streams from VRChat the majority of the time. Her preferred categories of content are video games and streamer challenges (such as You Laugh - You Lose, You Scream - You Lose, etc.) These streamer challenges usually entail performing a randomly selected \\\"punishment\\\", with some of the punishments being labeled as \\\"jackpots\\\" while most others are ideas from her community on Discord.</font></p><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 6px 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; overflow: auto; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"History\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">History</font></span></h2><h3 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; overflow: initial; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"Early_history\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Early history</font></span></h3><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">Prior to becoming a streamer, Filian simply hung out in VRChat with her friends, who eventually convinced her to start streaming.</font></p><h3 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; overflow: initial; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"2021\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">2021</font></span></h3><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">On 18 April, Filian started steaming on Twitch.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-12\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Filian#cite_note-12\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[9]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">On 27 July, she achieved affiliate status on Twitch.</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">On 27 October, Filian reached partner status on Twitch.</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">On 5 November, she announced her first Subathon.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-13\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Filian#cite_note-13\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[10]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">On 11 November, she reached 10,000 followers on Twitch.</font></p><h3 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; overflow: initial; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"2022\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">2022</font></span></h3><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">On 3 February, Filian reached 50,000 followers on Twitch.</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">On 6 March, she reached 100,000 followers on Twitch.</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">On 21 March, she reached 100,000 subscribers on YouTube<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-14\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Filian#cite_note-14\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[11]</a></sup>, earning her a Silver Play Button.dsadasdasdasdasd</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">sdsadasdadasdasdOn 28 September, she reached 1,000,000 subscribers on YouTube,<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-16\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"text-wrap: nowrap; box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Filian#cite_note-16\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[13]</a></sup>&nbsp;earning her a Gold Play Button.<br></font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#33aaf3\\\">On 13 December, she reached 500,000 followers on Twitch.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-17\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Filian#cite_note-17\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[14]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><br></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><br></p>', 'http://localhost/api-blog/uploads/28c9ac60-3c15-11ef-b977-0c4de43b1664.jpg', 'BJozVR4D', NULL);
