(190, 'Gawr Gura', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\"><b style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\">Gawr Gura</b>&nbsp;(がうる・ぐら) is a female English-speaking Virtual YouTuber associated with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Hololive\" title=\"Hololive\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">hololive</a>, debuting in 2020 as part of hololive English first generation \"-Myth-\" alongside&nbsp;<a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Ninomae_Ina%27nis\" title=\"Ninomae Ina\'nis\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">Ninomae Ina\'nis</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Takanashi_Kiara\" title=\"Takanashi Kiara\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">Takanashi Kiara</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Watson_Amelia\" title=\"Watson Amelia\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">Watson Amelia</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Mori_Calliope\" title=\"Mori Calliope\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">Mori Calliope</a>.</font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">Gura is currently the most subscribed VTuber worldwide with over 4 million YouTube subscribers, taking the #1 spot from industry pioneer&nbsp;<a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Kizuna_Ai\" title=\"Kizuna Ai\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">Kizuna AI</a>&nbsp;in 2021.<br><br></font></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 6px 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; overflow: auto; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Personality\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">Personality</font></span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">Gura is friendly and readily likeable, and often amuses her viewers with foolish antics. She has no sense of direction, often misspells and mispronounces words, has trouble remembering her own age, and consistently fails to solve basic math problems, leading viewers to affectionately call her a \"dum shark\". Memorably, one viewer declared that \"Gura has a heart of gold and a head of bone.\"</font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">She can also be lazy at times. She often forgets about perishable items until they start to rot, and eats baby food \"because you don\'t have to cook it... [or] chew on it.\"</font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">However, despite her poor math and spelling skills, Gura is quick-witted, clever, and has vast knowledge of Shark Facts. When questioned on why she was not \"boing boing,\" she excused it by claiming that she was \"hydrodynamic.\" Her skill with fast-paced rhythm games is exceptional, and she is highly ambitious. She also occasionally makes lewd jokes, and is familiar with modern meme culture, which she references often.</font></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 6px 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; overflow: auto; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">Appearance</font></span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">Gawr Gura is very short, reaching around 141 cm (4\'7\"). She has a slim body type. She has white, light silver-like hair with baby blue and cobalt blue strands, along with short pigtails on either side of her head, tied with diamond-shaped, shark-faced hair ties. She has cyan pupils, and sharp, shark-like teeth. She can wear a dark cerulean-blue hood in the shape of a shark\'s head.</font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">She wears an oversized, dark cerulean-blue hoodie that fades into white on her arm sleeves and hem, two yellow strings in the shape of an \"x\" that connect the front part of her white hoodie hood, a shark mouth designed on her hoodie waist with a zipper, gray hoodie drawstrings with two black circles on each of them, and two pockets on the left and right sides of her hoodie waist with white fish bone designs on them.</font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">She also wears a gray shirt under her hoodie. She wears dark blue socks, white shoes with pale baby blue shoe tongues, black shoelaces, gray velcro patches on the vamps, and thick, black soles. She wields a sapphire-blue trident and has a cyan shark tail. The upper lobe of Gura\'s caudal fin, the top part of her tail, is sewn up with gray stitches because of a rock that fell on it while she was in a deep sea trench. The lower lobe of Gura\'s caudal fin, the bottom part of her tail, has three bite marks, which she forgot the cause of.</font></p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 6px 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; overflow: auto; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">History</font></span></h2><h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; overflow: initial; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Background\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">Background</font></span></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">On 23 April 2020, following the success of the Japanese-language&nbsp;<a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Hololive\" title=\"Hololive\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">hololive</a>&nbsp;VTuber group, Cover Corporation announced auditions for English-speaking members.<sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-10\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[10]</a></sup>&nbsp;The initial round of auditions ran until 24 May.<sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-11\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[11]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">Gura first encountered hololive via&nbsp;<a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Shirakami_Fubuki\" title=\"Shirakami Fubuki\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">Shirakami Fubuki</a>\'s&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\">Say! Fanfare!</i>, which appeared as a song in Muse Dash. She did not find out what hololive was until later, and decided to apply after learning of the hololive English auditions via Twitter. Her initial audition video was over the top, which she scrapped in favor of one that better represented her personality. She made it to a second round of auditions, followed by a third round normally consisting of a video call, which Gura actually declined. Despite this, she was selected to join hololive.<sup id=\"cite_ref-12\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-12\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[12]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">During her audition, Gura drew a cute character in a \"power stance\" with their hands on their hips, which she credited as setting a good impression. Gura recalls being asked about the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SCP_Foundation\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"wikipedia:SCP Foundation\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">SCP Foundation</a>, a wiki of articles describing fictional artifacts and beings, although she had to admit that she didn\'t know what it was.<sup id=\"cite_ref-13\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-13\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[13]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">The members of -Myth- began training around June 2020, three months before their debut.<sup id=\"cite_ref-14\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-14\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[14]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">Gawr Gura\'s design was known to other members of holoEN as early as 2 July 2020, when Amelia Watson drew the first ever piece of Gawr Gura fanart.<sup id=\"cite_ref-15\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-15\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[15]</a></sup>&nbsp;This was not the finalized design, however, and an unspecified design change was made before Gura\'s debut.<sup id=\"cite_ref-yt-m5wfUscXJOw_16-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-yt-m5wfUscXJOw-16\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[16]</a></sup>&nbsp;Internal pre-debut test streams were conducted between all members of hololive English, where in one case a bug caused Gura to spawn in without any clothes.</font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">Gura\'s YouTube channel and Twitter account were created on 16 July 2020.</font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">On 8 September 2020,<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\">[<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/converter.html?iso=20200909T03030000&amp;p1=137&amp;p2=1243&amp;p3=64&amp;p4=179&amp;p5=136&amp;p6=195&amp;p7=248&amp;p8=152\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">TZ</a>]</sup>&nbsp;Gawr Gura was first revealed in a short&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/8c4_22LjGQo\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">promotional video</a>&nbsp;alongside the other four members of hololive -Myth-. A simultaneous announcement was made at the hololive Twitter account, and the hololive English Twitter account.<sup id=\"cite_ref-17\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-17\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[17]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-18\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-18\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[18]</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-19\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-19\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[19]</a></sup>&nbsp;At the same time, Gura made her first tweet, famously consisting of the single letter \"a.\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-gawrguratweet_20-0\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-gawrguratweet-20\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[20]</a></sup></font></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; overflow: initial; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Debut\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">Debut</font></span></h4><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">Gura\'s&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://youtu.be/dBK0gKW61NU\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">debut stream</a>&nbsp;was scheduled for 12 September 2020 at 2PM PDT,<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\">[<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/converter.html?iso=20200912T22000000&amp;p1=137&amp;p2=1243&amp;p3=64&amp;p4=179&amp;p5=136&amp;p6=195&amp;p7=248&amp;p8=152\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">TZ</a>]</sup>&nbsp;although she was 12 minutes and 32 seconds late to her own debut stream due to a technical issue. She was the fourth of the five original members of hololive English to debut on the same day. Over 45,000 viewers tuned in to watch the event, in which she wowed viewers with a rendition of Tatsuro Yamashita\'s 1980 city pop single&nbsp;<i style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\">Ride on Time</i>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-21\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-21\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[21]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">In a six-month review of her debut, she described being so nervous that she could feel her heart beat in her head, and had stomach problems as she was too nervous to eat before the stream. Prior to the stream, she watched the debut videos of a number of hololive Japan streamers in order to prepare.<sup id=\"cite_ref-yt-m5wfUscXJOw_16-1\" class=\"reference\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\"><a href=\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura#cite_note-yt-m5wfUscXJOw-16\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">[16]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font color=\"#3367d1\">The debut events were concluded with the first hololive English collaboration event at 6:35PM PDT,<sup style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\">[<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/converter.html?iso=20200913T02350000&amp;p1=137&amp;p2=1243&amp;p3=64&amp;p4=179&amp;p5=136&amp;p6=195&amp;p7=248&amp;p8=152\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\">TZ</a>]</sup>&nbsp;in which Gura streamed together with the other four members of hololive English.</font></p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></p>', 'http://localhost/api-blog/uploads/hq720.jpg', 'Klk8fw9U', NULL);
