(191, 'Mori Calliope', '<font color=\\\"#d90202\\\"><b style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">Mori Calliope</b><span style=\\\"font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">&nbsp;(森 カリオペ) is a female English-speaking Virtual YouTuber associated with&nbsp;</span><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Hololive\\\" title=\\\"Hololive\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">hololive</a><span style=\\\"font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">, debuting in 2020 as part of hololive English first generation \\\"-Myth-\\\" alongside&nbsp;</span><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Ninomae_Ina%27nis\\\" title=\\\"Ninomae Ina\\\'nis\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">Ninomae Ina\\\'nis</a><span style=\\\"font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">,&nbsp;</span><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Takanashi_Kiara\\\" title=\\\"Takanashi Kiara\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">Takanashi Kiara</a><span style=\\\"font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">,&nbsp;</span><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Watson_Amelia\\\" title=\\\"Watson Amelia\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">Watson Amelia</a><span style=\\\"font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Gawr_Gura\\\" title=\\\"Gawr Gura\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">Gawr Gura</a><span style=\\\"font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\">.</span></font><div class=\\\"tabber wds-tabber\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow: hidden; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><div class=\\\"wds-tab__content wds-is-current\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><div style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; height: auto;\\\"><table class=\\\"article-table\\\" width=\\\"100%\\\" data-index-number=\\\"1\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; background: rgba(var(--theme-page-dynamic-color-1--rgb),.02); border: 0 var(--theme-border-color); border-collapse: collapse; margin: 1em 1em 1em 0px;\\\"><tbody style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit;\\\"><tr style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit;\\\"><td style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); padding: 6px 12px;\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">The Grim Reaper\\\'s first apprentice. Due to modern medical care causing a decline in the reaping business, Calliope decided to become a VTuber to harvest souls instead. It seems that the ascended souls of the people who are vaporized by the wholesome interactions between VTubers go to her as well.</font><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.75;\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">That being said, despite the image her hardcore vocals and manner of speech gives off, she\\\'s actually a gentle-hearted girl who cares greatly for her friends.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-5\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Mori_Calliope#cite_note-5\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration-line: none; transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[5]</a></sup></font></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 6px 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; overflow: auto; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"Personality\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">Personality</font></span></h2><div><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\"><br></font></span></div><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">The Grim Reaper\\\'s apprentice has displayed throughout her streams, guest appearances, and music to a have cool, yet serious personality, with a timid side being seen when interacting with others for the first time, such as her senpais. Calli\\\'s cool attitude can be clearly observed in most of her streams, as she tries her best to impress her fans with her musical talent and occasional gaming skills.</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">However, she is not afraid to get serious about topics that may be on her mind, and engages in thoughtful discussions with viewers. This combination of a relaxed yet serious personality has earned her the admiration of not only her fans, but also the other hololive talents as well.</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">However, Calli\\\'s playful side comes out more evidently during collaborations with her genmates, displaying a side of Calli which viewers don\\\'t regularly experience. Calli still remains above all an avid hard worker who is regularly working on projects behind the scenes, often not sleeping for long periods of time. Despite the challenges that she may face while working on these projects, each one is very much rewarded and appreciated by her fans each time a new original song or cover is released.</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">Calliope is equally excited by both rapping and \\\"reaping.\\\" Her favorite weapons include her scythe (nicknamed \\\"Ricky\\\") and the flail, a medieval weapon made from a spiked metal ball on a chain.</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">Calliope is noted for having one of the most lowest pitched voices in hololive, even more so than likes of&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Nekomata_Okayu\\\" title=\\\"Nekomata Okayu\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">Nekomata Okayu</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Tokoyami_Towa\\\" title=\\\"Tokoyami Towa\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">Tokoyami Towa</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/A-chan\\\" title=\\\"A-chan\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">A-chan</a>. Although fluent in English, Calliope often fails to understand current modes of speech, such as the use of contractions or modern slang. She is easily flustered by romance, leading some to call her the \\\"tsundereaper.\\\"</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">When not on camera, however, she is described as air-headed and hopelessly forgetful. Kiara has mentioned that she frequently misplaces things despite leaving them in an obvious place, like leaving her cellphone in her jacket. She also works exceptionally hard, perhaps too much so.</font></p><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 6px 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; overflow: auto; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"Appearance\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">Appearance</font></span></h2><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">She has long, straight pink hair with a small black crown with a transparent veil and pink eyes. She has a black cape with sharp white teeth.</font></p><h2 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-border-color); border-left: 0px; border-image: initial; margin: 18px 0px 9px; padding: 6px 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 500; overflow: auto; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"History\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">History</font></span></h2><h3 style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px 12px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; font-family: var(--theme-page-headings-font),rubik,helvetica,arial,sans-serif; line-height: 1.25; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 500; overflow: initial; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><span class=\\\"mw-headline\\\" id=\\\"Background\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial;\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">Background</font></span></h3><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">On 23 April 2020, following the success of the Japanese-language&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Hololive\\\" title=\\\"Hololive\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">hololive</a>&nbsp;VTuber group, Cover Corporation announced auditions for English-speaking members.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-7\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Mori_Calliope#cite_note-7\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[7]</a></sup>&nbsp;The initial round of auditions ran until 24 May.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-8\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Mori_Calliope#cite_note-8\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[8]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">Mori Calliope first heard of hololive after seeing clips on YouTube, particularly the infamous&nbsp;<a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Natsuiro_Matsuri\\\" title=\\\"Natsuiro Matsuri\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">Natsuiro Matsuri</a>&nbsp;band-aid story.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-9\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Mori_Calliope#cite_note-9\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[9]</a></sup>&nbsp;She heard of the hololive English audition from friends. She began watching hololive videos in her work breaks to familiarize herself with the other members, and became excited at the possibility of joining them. Calli had previously spent several years making music with an audience of no more than twenty people.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-10\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Mori_Calliope#cite_note-10\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[10]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">Calli auditioned by describing her best traits and skills and taking a professional tone. She credits her success to her hard work and willingness to take chances on new opportunities. After she was selected, it took some time for Calli to accept that she had been successful.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-11\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Mori_Calliope#cite_note-11\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[11]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">The members of -Myth- began training around June 2020, three months before their debut.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-12\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Mori_Calliope#cite_note-12\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[12]</a></sup></font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">Calli\\\'s YouTube channel was created on 16 July, and her Twitter account was created in the same month.</font></p><p style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 24px 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; font-family: rubik, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; text-align: start; white-space-collapse: collapse; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\\\"><font color=\\\"#d90202\\\">On 8 September 2020,<sup style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\">[<a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\\\" class=\\\"external text\\\" href=\\\"https://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/converter.html?iso=20200909T03030000&amp;p1=137&amp;p2=1243&amp;p3=64&amp;p4=179&amp;p5=136&amp;p6=195&amp;p7=248&amp;p8=152\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">TZ</a>]</sup>&nbsp;Mori Calliope was first revealed in a short&nbsp;<a target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\\\" class=\\\"external text\\\" href=\\\"https://youtu.be/8c4_22LjGQo\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">promotional video</a>&nbsp;alongside the other four members of hololive -Myth-. A simultaneous announcement was made at the hololive Twitter account, and the hololive English Twitter account.<sup id=\\\"cite_ref-13\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Mori_Calliope#cite_note-13\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[13]</a></sup><sup id=\\\"cite_ref-14\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Mori_Calliope#cite_note-14\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--theme-link-decoration); transition: color 0.3s; line-height: inherit;\\\">[14]</a></sup><sup id=\\\"cite_ref-15\\\" class=\\\"reference\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; unicode-bidi: isolate; text-wrap: nowrap; font-size: 10px; line-height: 0;\\\"><a href=\\\"https://virtualyoutuber.fandom.com/wiki/Mori_Calliope#cite_note-15\\\" style=\\\"box-sizing: inherit; border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: initial; text-decoration: var(--the